            <title>2.1.1</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 22:23:04 -0400</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>30</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.1.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <enclosure url="https://data.getwhisky.app/Releases/v2.1.1/Whisky.zip" length="4727899" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="a/EwLmqR8DSPb0M+rZDeTketkkOCuqIkDl36C2MKabYHmUAciF6xYI4gkOhFe7ucdVmzy3fZlp0esV24RFonDQ=="/>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>New Features:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>New settings window to allow you to configure settings like Whisky's update behaviour</li>
                    <li>WhiskyKit is now a Swift Package, allowing it to be integrated into other projects easily</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Quality of Life:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Removed some unused dependencies</li>
                    <li>All in-app internet requests will now be made to Whisky's server, eliminating the need to use a VPN to update Whisky for users in mainland China</li>
                    <li>Better in-app help menu with quick links for Whisky's Website, Discord, and GitHub</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Bug Fixes:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Significantly reduced the memory footprint of Whisky</li>
                    <li>Fixed a crash that would occur with certain programs and bottles</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Full Changelog:</h2> <a href="https://github.com/Whisky-App/Whisky/compare/v2.1.0...v2.1.1">https://github.com/Whisky-App/Whisky/compare/v2.1.0...v2.1.1</a>
            ]]></description>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.1.0</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 10:47:53 -0400</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>29</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
