            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>New Features:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Added <a href="https://github.com/marzent/wine-msync"><strong>MSync</strong></a>, a Mac-specific implementation of Wine sync, which greatly improves FPS in CPU-bound applications (GPTK needs to be re-downloaded)</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Bug Fixes:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Added a minimum window size to Whisky's main window</li>
                    <li>Fixed programs starting from pins not using arguments and environment variables</li>
                    <li>Fixed an issue where Retina Mode toggle would fail on other languages if the key didn't exist</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Full Changelog:</h2> <a href="https://github.com/Whisky-App/Whisky/compare/v2.0.2...v2.1.0">https://github.com/Whisky-App/Whisky/compare/v2.0.2...v2.1.0</a>
            ]]></description>
